'''托德莫登'''（Todmorden）<ref>See page 828 of John C. Wells's LPD.  Also, see [http://www.phon.ucl.ac.uk/home/wells/blog0804b.htm 25 April 2008] {{Wayback|url=http://www.phon.ucl.ac.uk/home/wells/blog0804b.htm |date=20200928031854 }} and [http://phonetic-blog.blogspot.com/2010/01/bessacarr.html 29 January 2010] {{Wayback|url=http://phonetic-blog.blogspot.com/2010/01/bessacarr.html |date=20210123055918 }}</ref><ref>Peter Wright, ''A Yorkshireman's Dictionary'', page 8</ref>是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]的一個城鎮和民政教區<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadPage.do?pageId=1003&tc=1189606186976&a=7&b=790751&c=todmorden&d=16&e=15&g=380116&i=1001x1003x1004&m=0&enc=1 |title=Census 2001 – Todmorden CP (Parish) |publisher=Office for National Statistics |work=Neighbourhood Statistics |accessdate=12 September 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303183709/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadPage.do?pageId=1003&tc=1189606186976&a=7&b=790751&c=todmorden&d=16&e=15&g=380116&i=1001x1003x1004&m=0&enc=1 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，位於[[西約克郡|西約克郡]]，距[[曼徹斯特|曼徹斯特]]有17英里。2001年有人口14,941人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790270|publisher=Office for National Statistics|title=Census 2001 : Parish Headcounts : Calderdale|accessdate=2 September 2009|work=Neighbourhood Statistics|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303195547/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/viewFullDataset.do?instanceSelection=03070&productId=779&$ph=60_61&datasetInstanceId=3070&startColumn=1&numberOfColumns=8&containerAreaId=790270|archive-date=2016-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，2011年增加至15,481人<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11129755&c=Todmorden&d=16&e=62&g=6370497&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1456230375849&enc=1|title=Town population 2011|accessdate=23 February 2016|publisher=Office for National Statistics|work=Neighbourhood Statistics|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314143855/http://www.neighbourhood.statistics.gov.uk/dissemination/LeadKeyFigures.do?a=7&b=11129755&c=Todmorden&d=16&e=62&g=6370497&i=1001x1003x1032x1004&m=0&r=1&s=1456230375849&enc=1|archive-date=2016-03-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。這一地名首次出現是在1641年。

